{"tid":1909594,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"柳喜烈的人生巔峰！我活到這個年紀竟然還能遇到這種好事","createTime":"2020-03-04T05:32:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-04T13:42:57.000Z","uid":74065,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a93c0128b9b62fda9cdce31f79c8ea58aff0cf00","tid":1909594,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T05:32:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_ad3e294a96b95efb851ca8ade4c53432/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-02-21/124482-817324.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_ad3e294a96b95efb851ca8ade4c53432%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-02-21%2F124482-817324.png&h=b9b863ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n女團只為你一個人表演是什麼感覺？ 這就要問柳喜烈了。<br />\n<br />\n最近GFRIEND參與了綜藝節目《柳喜烈的寫生簿》錄製，因為新型冠狀病毒的蔓延，節目組最終決定取消旁聽觀眾的參與，僅有主持人、嘉賓和工作人員到場。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_e5bd9d6bb7f6ce13e57f20397d5f7f18/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-02-21/124482-817326.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_e5bd9d6bb7f6ce13e57f20397d5f7f18%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-02-21%2F124482-817326.png&h=83807a18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_bbf1e3f294b13047adb96144d383b50d/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-02-21/124482-817330.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_bbf1e3f294b13047adb96144d383b50d%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-02-21%2F124482-817330.png&h=b2285723&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n和以往充滿粉絲尖叫聲和笑聲的片場不同，少了粉絲和觀眾的錄製現場顯得尤為冷清。一開場柳喜烈就說明瞭情況，求得眾人的諒解，更是強調「走過空蕩蕩的演播廳，突然就體會到大家是多麼的珍貴，很想你們。 」<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_97febd2b9a0437f23ddbda46b56b5bb0/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-02-21/124482-817327.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_97febd2b9a0437f23ddbda46b56b5bb0%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-02-21%2F124482-817327.png&h=8264ba98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n柳喜烈的失落和沮喪伴隨著GFRIEND的登場而消散，GFRIEND只為他一人表演，秒變粉絲的柳熙烈也在台下又唱又跳，原本冷清的現場也漸漸熱了起來。 尤其是臉上也浮現了大大的笑容，激動得直說：「我活到這個年紀竟然還能遇到這種好事~」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_891804b1fe508e72e35b7f2e13ff228b/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-02-21/124482-817331.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_891804b1fe508e72e35b7f2e13ff228b%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-02-21%2F124482-817331.png&h=099f1036&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NVSL2Sde-Ow\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DNVSL2Sde-Ow&d=VxC68O7S0S1nNKmf4pYeIZNY2w26zYPSLCKwhaLFqs8%3D&h=793c9291\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NVSL2Sde-Ow</a>"},{"pid":"b9b1cdc4b7012293452843895c85ddc1dfbd42c4","tid":1909594,"uid":132174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T05:34:33.000Z","msg":"十大好人好事系列<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a652f22b90f6913bb54014fc3caf67d87bf59ab","tid":1909594,"uid":172668,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T05:34:55.000Z","msg":"又改名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n豬friend不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1306ca49b6c3775e90b653b28d6724197a9b23a5","tid":1909594,"uid":74065,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5a652f22b90f6913bb54014fc3caf67d87bf59ab","tid":1909594,"uid":172668,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T05:34:55.000Z","msg":"又改名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n豬friend不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T05:40:23.000Z","msg":"躝啦老女人"},{"pid":"01e34a6d08256622ecff03e80bedd0bd2de03898","tid":1909594,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5a652f22b90f6913bb54014fc3caf